'''Serowe''' ke motse mogolo wa morafe wa [[Bangwato]] ba kgosi kgolo ya bone e leng Kgosi Seretse Khama Ian Khama.
Serowe o itsege thata fa ele motse mogolo mo Botswana morago ga motse mogolo wa Bakwena ebong Molepolole ebile ke one motse mogolo wa Bamangwato.Serowe o itsege thata ka ele one motse yoo bontsi jwa  botautona ba Botswana ba tlholegeng teng.[[Category:Botswana]]

